items.name: Kiques
items.description: Kiques is a full-stack sneaker store web app built with Flask, React, and SQLAlchemy. It allows users to browse and manage sneakers, with data pulled from an API. The app features a responsive UI powered by Bootstrap and is designed for easy expansion with future features like authentication.
